medigram.medigram

Class Problem

  • java.lang.Object
    • medigram.medigram.Problem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Problem>

    public class Problem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Problem>
    Represents a problem that the user is having. Problems can have a title, a description, a date the problem started, a body location, a list of records, and a list of photos.
    See Also:
